{"sections":{"main":{"type":"template--page","disabled":true,"settings":{"page_title_enabled":true,"page_width":"narrow"}},"slideshow_NkT7FD":{"type":"slideshow","blocks":{"image_HVxpn6":{"type":"image","settings":{"h1_heading":"Herencia 1920","title":"Sabor, historia y emoción","text":"Más de un siglo creando momentos inolvidables","first_button_link":"","first_button_label":"","second_button_link":"","second_button_label":"","buttons_style":"filled","override_button_colors":false,"button-background":"#e68819","button-text":"#ffffff","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Enrique_Garcia_y_Javier_Garcia_1.jpg","text_position":"bottom_left","desktop-caption-heading-size":24,"desktop-caption-body-text-size":14,"mobile_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Enrique_Garcia_y_Javier_Garcia_1.jpg","mobile_text_position":"bottom","mobile-caption-heading-size":20,"mobile-caption-body-text-size":14,"caption-text":"#ffffff","image_overlay":"#1a1a1a","image_overlay_opacity":15}}},"block_order":["image_HVxpn6"],"name":"t:sections.image--slideshow.presets.name","settings":{"desktop_height":"full_screen","mobile_height":"extra_large","slide_navigation_style":"bars","slide_transition_delay":5,"section_width":"full","section_padding_top":0,"section_padding_bottom":0}},"rich_text_6JGMpY":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_k6Lqtw":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Los pilares de nuestro legado","heading_tag":"h2","heading--text-size":24,"heading_bottom_spacing":20}},"richtext_jPa7MC":{"type":"richtext","settings":{"text":"<p>En cada loncha de jamón ibérico y embutido de bellota vive nuestra historia: el legado de una familia y la herencia de una raza única y el privilegio de un entorno inigualable. No somos solo productores de ibéricos, somos guardianes de una tradición centenaria. Nuestra <strong>Herencia 1920 <\/strong>se fundamenta en tres pilares esenciales y cada pieza que elaboramos lleva consigo nuestra identidad y el compromiso con la excelencia.<\/p>","text_size":14,"text_bottom_spacing":20}}},"block_order":["heading_k6Lqtw","richtext_jPa7MC"],"name":"t:sections.text--rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"section_width":"narrow","text_alignment_desktop":"center","text_alignment_mobile":"center","section_padding_top":60,"section_padding_bottom":60,"colors":"light"}},"rich_text_QrBxAm":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_nmnLef":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Una historia centenaria que se saborea con el alma.","heading_tag":"span","heading--text-size":30,"heading_bottom_spacing":0}},"heading_gxmCfM":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Sumérgete en una experiencia sensorial única.","heading_tag":"span","heading--text-size":30,"heading_bottom_spacing":20}}},"block_order":["heading_nmnLef","heading_gxmCfM"],"name":"t:sections.text--rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"section_width":"narrow","text_alignment_desktop":"center","text_alignment_mobile":"center","section_padding_top":60,"section_padding_bottom":60,"colors":"dark"}},"rich_text_JKg68g":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_976Lgc":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Una familia dedicada al ibérico desde 1920","heading_tag":"h2","heading--text-size":24,"heading_bottom_spacing":20}},"richtext_CK9qec":{"type":"richtext","settings":{"text":"<p>Cuatro generaciones perfeccionado cada proceso, con la misma pasión del primer día<\/p>","text_size":14,"text_bottom_spacing":20}}},"block_order":["heading_976Lgc","richtext_CK9qec"],"name":"t:sections.text--rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"section_width":"narrow","text_alignment_desktop":"center","text_alignment_mobile":"center","section_padding_top":60,"section_padding_bottom":60,"colors":"white"}},"image_with_text_Nc67rU":{"type":"image-with-text","name":"t:sections.image--image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/BienvenidoGarcia_Fundador.png","layout":"left","reverse_order_mobile":false,"subheading":"GENERACIÓN I - El fundador","title":"1920: Bienvenido García - La semilla de una pasión","title_tag":"span","text":"<p>En 1920, nuestro bisabuelo Bienvenido sentó las bases de un sueño. Un hombre de campo con una visión clara: elaborar los mejores ibéricos respetando el producto y la tierra. Su trabajo y sus valores son la piedra angular sobre la que se construye todo.<\/p>","text_alignment":"left","text_overlapping_image":false,"button_link":"","button_label":"","buttons_style":"filled","override_button_colors":false,"button_background_color":"#e68819","button_text_color":"#ffffff","secondary_button_link":"","secondary_button_label":"","secondary_buttons_style":"outlined","override_secondary_button_colors":false,"secondary_button_background_color":"#ffffff","secondary_button_text_color":"#000000","button_layout":"inline","button_spacing":10,"section-width":"full","section_padding_top":0,"section_padding_bottom":0,"colors":"light"}},"image_with_text_4RGKrR":{"type":"image-with-text","name":"t:sections.image--image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Enrique_Garcia_Abuelo.jpg","layout":"right","reverse_order_mobile":false,"subheading":"GENERACIÓN II - El guardián de la tradición","title":"El legado continúa: la consolidación de un sueño","title_tag":"span","text":"<p>La segunda generación tomó el relevo con la responsabilidad de consolidar la tradición. Fueron años de crecimiento, de afianzar el \"saber hacer\" y de transmitir a sus hijos una cultura de trabajo donde la calidad siempre estaría por encima de todo.<\/p>","text_alignment":"left","text_overlapping_image":false,"button_link":"","button_label":"","buttons_style":"filled","override_button_colors":false,"button_background_color":"#e68819","button_text_color":"#ffffff","secondary_button_link":"","secondary_button_label":"","secondary_buttons_style":"outlined","override_secondary_button_colors":false,"secondary_button_background_color":"#ffffff","secondary_button_text_color":"#000000","button_layout":"inline","button_spacing":10,"section-width":"full","section_padding_top":0,"section_padding_bottom":0,"colors":"light"}},"image_with_text_iGUzBN":{"type":"image-with-text","name":"t:sections.image--image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Enrique_Garcia_y_Javier_Garcia_1.jpg","layout":"left","reverse_order_mobile":false,"subheading":"GENERACIÓN III - Los maestros del ibérico","title":"Enrique y Javier García: la perfección de la herencia","title_tag":"span","text":"<p>Crecimos entre secaderos y dehesas. Hoy, como tercera generación, seguimos fieles a ese legado, combinando la artesanía de siempre con las técnicas más innovadoras para ofrecer ibéricos con un sabor inolvidable y la garantía de un proceso cuidado al detalle.<\/p>","text_alignment":"left","text_overlapping_image":false,"button_link":"","button_label":"","buttons_style":"filled","override_button_colors":false,"button_background_color":"#e68819","button_text_color":"#ffffff","secondary_button_link":"","secondary_button_label":"","secondary_buttons_style":"outlined","override_secondary_button_colors":false,"secondary_button_background_color":"#ffffff","secondary_button_text_color":"#000000","button_layout":"inline","button_spacing":10,"section-width":"full","section_padding_top":0,"section_padding_bottom":0,"colors":"light"}},"image_with_text_yAjNzg":{"type":"image-with-text","name":"t:sections.image--image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Cuarta_Generacion_Herencia.jpg","layout":"right","reverse_order_mobile":false,"subheading":"GENERACIÓN IV - El futuro del legado","title":"El futuro: una mirada al origen respetando la herencia 1920","title_tag":"span","text":"<p>La cuarta generación representa el futuro, un futuro que mira con respeto al pasado. Con la misma mentalidad de ganaderos, continuamos con el ciclo cerrado de elaboración que mantiene viva nuestra esencia artesanal, garantizando que la historia de Enrique García siga contándose durante, al menos, 100 años más.<\/p>","text_align